{
  "stem": "5551.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They clubbed them to death in the street, both of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they succumbed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They died in an embrace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "None of them ever lived a day without the other-- courtesy of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You were led to this story unwillingly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it is a story I cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me first tell you-- maybe I better start with Germany where I was born.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- my father was a small merchant of clothes-- workmen's clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a small store on [NON-ENGLISH] '39, in Breslau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was born there and went to the regional public school there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Few Jews, and the rest of the children were all German children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were friends with the German children that I went to school with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My closest friend was a German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Manfred Buchhalt-- Manfred Buchhalt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] We had a generous mutual social life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went to school together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We played together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We came to one another's home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And our parents were friendly on both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Until his older brother-- his name was Wolfgang-- joined-- he was at the time already in college-- and he joined the Hitler Youth-- the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This was the first time I saw Wolfgang in a brown uniform with a swastika and so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And soon thereafter-- I remember it well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even though Wolfgang, in the beginning, was making me comfortable-- I'm now talking about 1932, before the takeover of Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He thought-- he himself thought, honestly-- that it doesn't have anything to do with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was too young and too foolish to understand what is developing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
